<h1 class="display-4 text-center mt-5">Zhengzhou Yutong Group Co., Ltd.</h1>
<p class="h6 fw-normal text-center mt-2">
    Yutong (officially Zhengzhou Yutong Group Co., Ltd.) is a Chinese manufacturer of commercial vehicles, especially electric buses, headquartered in Zhengzhou, Henan. 
    Yutong also has businesses in construction machinery, real estate, and other investments. As of 2026, Yutong is recognized as the world's largest bus 
    and coach manufacturer by volume, producing approximately 150,000 vehicles annually. Yutong's comprehensive lineup spans across various sectors, including city buses, 
    long distance coaches, tourist coaches, commuters, school buses and special-purpose vehicles. Galleries below are some of its notable bus models exported in the Philippines.
</p>

